---
slug: api/reviews/list-results
format: json
method: get
searchable: false
metadata: {
    "status": "published",
    "api_endpoint_name": "Reviews | List Results (AJAX)"
}
---
{% comment %}
    AJAX endpoint for the PDP Reviews tab pagination. Returns the rendered
    reviews list + pager for a product/page so the tab can swap just the list
    instead of reloading the page. Approved reviews only (query filters status).

    Params:
    - product : product uuid (reviewed_product)
    - page    : page number (default 1)
{% endcomment %}
{%- assign page = context.params.page | default: 1 | plus: 0 -%}
{%- assign per_page = context.params.per_page | default: 5 | plus: 0 -%}
{%- assign product_uuid = context.params.product | strip -%}

{%- graphql reviews = 'modules/ecommerce/reviews/get_reviews', reviewed_product: product_uuid, page: page, size: per_page | dig: 'items' -%}

{%- capture html -%}
{%- include 'modules/ecommerce/reviews/review_list', reviews: reviews -%}
{%- endcapture -%}

{
    "html": {{ html | json }},
    "totalCount": {{ reviews.total_entries | default: 0 }},
    "pageNumber": {{ page }},
    "pageSize": {{ per_page }}
}
